'''''Sudden Fiction (Continued): 60 New Short Stories''''' is a collection of [[short story|short stories]] published in 1996. It was compiled and edited by Robert Shapard and James Thomas. It is a follow-up to ''Sudden Fiction International'' (1989) and ''Sudden Fiction - American Short-Short Stories.''

Notable authors in ''Sudden Fiction (Continued)'' include [[William Keepers Maxwell, Jr.|William Maxwell]], [[Margaret Atwood]], [[Don DeLillo]], [[Mark Richard]], [[Molly Giles]], [[Bruce Holland Rogers]], [[Barry Peters (author)|Barry Peters]], [[Andrew Lam]], and [[Judy Troy]].

